<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='541000' id='t-541000'>But this last time, just coming round, right now,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='545000' id='t-545000'>suddenly, there'd be huge changes in the environment,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='550000' id='t-550000'>in the concentration of people,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='553000' id='t-553000'>and it was just unbelievable, the amount of -- all the change in it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='565000' id='t-565000'>I wanted to -- well, one of the biggest changes is, 200 years ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570000' id='t-570000'>we began using coal from underground, which has a lot of pollution,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='576000' id='t-576000'>and 100 years ago, began getting gasoline from underground,</span>
