<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='586000' id='t-586000'>will reach its limit in about ten years, and then go down,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='591000' id='t-591000'>and we wonder what's going to happen with transportation.</span>
</span>
</p>
