<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='752000' id='t-752000'>claims all energy on Earth can be derived, for every country,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='757000' id='t-757000'>from solar energy and water, and so on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='765000' id='t-765000'>You don't need to dig down for these chemicals,</span>
