<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='786000' id='t-786000'>no longer subject to the checks and balances inherent in nature,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='790000' id='t-790000'>have grown in population, technology and intelligence</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='793000' id='t-793000'>to a position of terrible power. We, now, wield the paintbrush.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='797000' id='t-797000'>We're in charge. It's frightening.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='801000' id='t-801000'>And I do a painting every 20 or 25 years. This is the last one.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='806000' id='t-806000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='808000' id='t-808000'>And [it] shows the Earth in a time flag: on the right,</span>
