<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1143000' id='t-1143000'>I'll give you a demonstration of how it works.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1145000' id='t-1145000'>The idea is that it soars on the lift over your body, like a seagull soaring on a cliff.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1151000' id='t-1151000'>As the wind comes up, it has to go over the cliff, so</span>
